&lt;p&gt;Here, MOP is written as &lt;strong&gt;NNQ &lt;/strong&gt;as per the logic.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence,&amp;nbsp;the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;NNQ&amp;quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
